queries.sql: SELECT `rem`.*, `read`.*, `users`.`id`, `users`.`firstname`, `users`.`lastname` FROM `reminder` as `rem` JOIN `remind_read` as `read` ON `read`.`rem_id` = `rem`.`rem_id` JOIN `bo_users` as `users` ON `read`.`user_id` = `users`.`id` WHERE `read`.`user_id` = '100' AND `rem`.`status` = '1' GROUP BY `read`.`rem_id` ORDER BY `read`.`read_id` DESC

SELECT `rem`.*, `read`.*, `users`.`id`, `users`.`firstname`, `users`.`lastname` FROM `reminder` as `rem` JOIN `remind_read` as `read` ON `read`.`rem_id` = `rem`.`rem_id` JOIN `bo_users` as `users` ON `read`.`user_id` = `users`.`id` WHERE `read`.`for` = '100' AND `rem`.`remind_date` <= '2023-04-11' AND `rem`.`remind_date` >= '2023-01-11' AND `rem`.`status` = '1' GROUP BY `read`.`rem_id` ORDER BY `read`.`read_id` DESC
